### Summary of System State

The current codebase is in a highly professional state: it is panic-free, thread-safe, and memory-bounded. The remaining items are optimizations focused on **fault isolation** and **cancellation safety**—ensuring that failures in one subsystem (Firebase network stability) do not degrade the performance of separate subsystems (the local game capture engine and the Tauri configuration UI).